        <div class="agenda-body">
          <div class="agenda-content">
            <p style="text-align: left;"><strong style="color: #FDB631">.access: </strong> aims at stimulating a global social change by applying a strength-based approach while dealing with the refugee phenomenon instead of perceiving them as pathetic vulnerable groups.</p>
            <p style="text-align: left;"><strong style="color: #FDB631">.access: </strong> aims mainly at creating an open source database for Refugees's professional profiles.</p>
          </div>
