      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-author">
      <div class="testimonial-user-name">
        <p style="text-align: left"><strong style="color: #FDB631">.access: </strong> aims at launching the first Humanitarian Internet Domain that stands for esatblishing a bi-directional communication path bewteen refugees and job markets.</p>
        <p style="text-align: left;"><strong style="color: #FDB631">.access: </strong> aims at launching an Association for Forced Migartion Workforce that will regulate and monitor the access of its members to job markets.</p>
