<div class="container">
  <div class="about-content margin-bottom">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h2><strong>-How it Works-</strong></h2>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-6">
            <%= image_tag"Selection_019.png"%>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xs-6">
            <p><strong>HOW IT WORKS:</strong>Launching .access is in itself a digital invitation to all refugees and companies to communicate with each other through our platform.</p>
            <p><strong>Companies</strong> are invited to display their own job vacancies and refugees can apply to them and wait for the decisions of the companies. Thus, there won't be any need for humanitarian organizations to facilitate that reach out or communication that usually requires several months or years.</p>
            <p><strong>Refugees</strong> can make urgent calls on our platform for specifying their needs for professional trainings and job opportunities, especially when their contracts with their humanitarian programs finish.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
